******
[2] False smut and blast - India (Telangana)
Date: Thu 26 Oct 2017 10:38 PM IST
Source: Telangana Today [edited]
https://telanganatoday.com/nalgonda-rice-blast-false-smut-toll-paddy


Rice blast and false smut diseases are likely to have an adverse impact on the paddy production in [Nalgonda] district as hundreds of acres have been affected by the fungal disease. Frequent and prolonged rains led to rice blast infection in most of the areas.

According to officials the disease would lead to reduction in the paddy production by 25 to 30 per cent. District Agricultural Advisory and Transfer of Technology Centre's (DATTC) Shailaja [said] that majority of farmers in the district had taken up cultivation [of] BPT and 1110 varieties of paddy, which were vulnerable to rice blast and false smut diseases.

[A] farmer said sprays suggested by the agricultural officers were not available in the market. Shops were selling gullible farmers low quality sprays.

